title: Asian-Style Glazed Beef & Sesame Fries with Cucumber Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: Tonight’s dinner takes beef rump and veg to new levels. As if beef rump glazed in honey and soy sauce wasn’t delicious enough, serving it alongside sesame fries and a Japanese slaw adds another flavour punch! A dollop of garlic aioli adds the perfect amount of creaminess to this irresistible dish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

